Interface IConfigurableContainer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IComplianceFilterSetContainer, IFilterContainer, IPriceStepTable, IPriceStepTableContainer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComplianceFilterSet, ComplianceFilterSetDictionary, PercentageFromAuctionPriceFilter, PercentageFromBestPriceFilter, PercentageFromLastPriceFilter, PercentageFromMarketPriceFilter, PercentageFromReferencePriceFilter, PriceStepTable, PriceStepTableDictionary, PriceToleranceTable

    public interface IConfigurableContainer
    An interface for objects that a) contain other objects and b) are constructed from a configuration file (or can be written to a configuration file).
